{"tid":1915163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"偽黃店Sharepapa食人血饅頭！！！","createTime":"2020-03-08T04:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T03:56:41.000Z","uid":121677,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a8badac57f4be3ae0cbacf116665d2bfff7315cc","tid":1915163,"uid":121677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:33:40.000Z","msg":"這間店的問題如下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 2月頭訂了口罩到今日還沒有，已經過了他們承諾的限期！<br />\n<br />\n2. 退款要收3%手續費，但問題根本是在消費者身上！是他們自己沒貨！<br />\n<br />\n3. 這間店根本沒貨就已經做廣告和網上上架賣貨，擺明騙消費者錢集資買貨。<br />\n<br />\n4. 遲遲未有口罩因為找不到便宜口罩，例如他們集資了100萬，要出貨20萬個口罩，每個口罩$5，那他們只會找每個口罩售價低於$5的供應，之後食差價賺錢！<br />\n<br />\n5. 因為口罩成本價低廉，可能不合乎安全標準，不能達到防菌功能。<br />\n<br />\n6. 這間網店的所有貨品價格全部高於其他ig店或其他網店價格."},{"pid":"7fd0129ad0d951bad560ce96e1e13a2a14991cf9","tid":1915163,"uid":121677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:34:36.000Z","msg":"推一推 等人睇到！！"},{"pid":"1856f97db49066c7a9aa0c9adc442d3a201d98f5","tid":1915163,"uid":121677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:35:15.000Z","msg":"推一推 等人睇到！！"},{"pid":"959368ace6f9f49894e44577c467e60cf21f8f0b","tid":1915163,"uid":57490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:42:56.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"cf15ac3891c51e9525be6878532eb7d1ff1954ca","tid":1915163,"uid":121677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"959368ace6f9f49894e44577c467e60cf21f8f0b","tid":1915163,"uid":57490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:42:56.000Z","msg":"幫推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:47:21.000Z","msg":"多謝 間野好pk"},{"pid":"5502ff60fb79e679bf4abd8d376abe4a0861f8e9","tid":1915163,"uid":121677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:58:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fad751d5010315a755e3104acf0d7d6cd276ff3","tid":1915163,"uid":121677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:59:21.000Z","msg":"sor手殘<br />\n<br />\n2. 退款要收3%手續費，但問題根本<strong>不</strong>是在